<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV74">
<l>taḷarntum muṟintum varutiraip pāyaṟ ṟiruneṭuṅkaṇ</l>
<l>vaḷarntu maṟivuṟṟum vaiyam viḻuṅkiyu mālvaraiyaik</l>
<l>kiḷarntu maṟitarak kīṇṭeṭut tāṉmuṭi cūṭutuḻā</l>
<l>yaḷaintuṇ ciṟupacun teṉṟalan tōvan tulākiṉṟatē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who slackened, gave way, closed [his] holy large eyes on a bed of oncoming waves,</l>
<l>had knowledge, swallowed the world, split, for it to emerge and be known,</l>
<l>[and] lifted the great mountain – mingling with [and] absorbing the Tulsi</l>
<l>he wears in [his] crown he comes [and] stirs a little fresh south wind, alas.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
